title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1992-03-18
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Wang Dang Doodle, Jack A Roe, It's All Over Now, Row Jimmy, Picasso Moon, Deal

Set 2

Eyes Of The World-> Corinna-> Playin' In The Band Reprise-> Uncle John's Band-> Jam*-> Drums-> Jam-> Wave To The Wind-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

*phil and Vince with Drums

reviews.review_text: Best recording of this show This is the only recording that isn't so keyboard heavy that you can't hear that guitars. The other versions of this show sound like an isolated track of just keyboards. Thank you for uploading this. The show would be wasted if it weren't for this recording. The rest don't do it justice.
